document_data.name: Sulaspra Delzuld
document_data.mainbody:
'''Sulaspra Delzuld''' was a woman of the [[Delzuld]] noble family of [[Cormyr]] in the mid–13th century [[DR]], living [[1241 DR]] to [[1276 DR]].

She married [[Gaspar Ammaeth]], and with him was the mother of [[Elduss Ammaeth]] and the grandmother of Duke [[Bhereu]] and Baron [[Thomdor]].<ref>
